{
  "stem": "27347.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We met them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandfather was a very pious Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And really, he was the only man I ever met that was so devoted to God with heart and soul.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the worst of times, he never doubted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was-- he had faith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my grandmother was a very smart lady.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't think she was exactly like my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was religious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I think she would have bent some rules if it was up to her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she was in so in awe of her husband and lived for him and took care of him that she did everything that was expected of her.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was a very loving mother, a very sacrificing mother, a mother that never needed anything, only for her children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My aunt was a businesswoman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She had several girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was a seamstress, a designer seamstress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She used to design clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, and, and they came from all the towns around there for dowry outfits and things like that to my aunt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was famous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She was one of the best.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so she was in business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was earning money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't know what my uncle did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I have absolutely no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they were very nice family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My cousin was lovely, very warm girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We became friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we stayed with my grandfather who shared the house with the rabbi of the town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The rabbi wouldn't share it with anyone except my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rebbe [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Moishele. ?] That's all I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's-- that's no family name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was introduced to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it-- I remember nights the Hasidim would sit together, dance, and talk and sing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like a men's club.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was funny.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
